 Question 3: String Rotation Checker

 ðŸ“˜ Scenario

You are implementing a password validation system.
The system must check whether a given password is a rotation of the original password.

---

 ðŸ§ª Test Cases

| String 1      | String 2      | Output  |
| ------------- | ------------- | ------- |
| waterbottle | erbottlewat | True  |
| abcde       | cdeab       | True  |
| abc         | acb         | False |

---

 ðŸ›  Java Methods

 length()
 contains()
 concat() or +

