 Question 5: Replace Substring

 ðŸ“˜ Scenario

You are developing a find-and-replace feature in a text editor.
The system must replace all occurrences of a given substring with another substring.

---

 ðŸ§ª Test Cases

| Input String | Target | Replacement | Output   |
| ------------ | ------ | ----------- | -------- |
| banana     | na   | xy        | baxyxy |
| abcabc     | abc  | x         | xx     |

---

 ðŸ›  Java Methods

 replace()
